{"tid":1616991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[正視聽]係緊急法唔係蒙面法","createTime":"2019-10-03T15:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T15:11:48.000Z","uid":24335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b125d9abfc8d9688f87f26af3e37bafacc38bd0e","tid":1616991,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=364996&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364996%26refer%3DShare&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=988f679a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364996%26refer%3DShare&h=ed1bdb15\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=364996&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】消息透露行政會議明日召開特別會議，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">商討引用緊急法臨時立法，包括反蒙面法及延長被捕人士拘留時間。</span></strong>立法會議員葛珮帆認為，立法有助減少蒙面破壞的人，法律界立法會議員郭榮鏗認為，一旦引用緊急法，港人自由會逐步被削弱。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好俾政府陰到, 依家係諗住出緊急法, 蒙面法只係其中一部分, 實行緊急法政府做乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"cd60dc738f07bb120c95be379460cb6301daa285","tid":1616991,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳 <br />\n<br />\n香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=34c0efa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"05ae10e3edc44ec9db511ae548f26af733e8e3da","tid":1616991,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:11:48.000Z","msg":"搵建制出黎開記招, spin落去蒙面法<br />\n實際上林奠引用緊急法避開立法會, 開外掛先係核彈<br />\n當然我想佢快D出核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}